Additionally, the paper involves transfer learning, which is a common topic in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multiple sub-domains also suggests that it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the paper deals with reducing the gap between domains, which could also make it relevant to the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) category.
